---
/*
====================================================
AdminReflectionEditor

Responsabilidad
Presentar el formulario editorial y la vista previa local de una reflexión.

Qué renderiza
Los grupos Idea principal, Imagen, Contenido y Publicación, además de un diálogo accesible de preview.

Datos que recibe
El nombre público del autor, usado como atribución predeterminada cuando la cita es propia.

Dependencias
Solo recibe configuración pública; el controlador de AdminDashboard conecta estos campos con servicios y Supabase.

Qué no debe hacer
No autentica, no consulta datos, no sube imágenes y no decide permisos administrativos.

Decisión de arquitectura
La preview comparte el estado vivo del formulario mediante data attributes. No crea una segunda página ni persiste
contenido temporal, por lo que permite revisar con fidelidad sin ampliar la superficie de seguridad del Admin.

Autor: Daniel Montesinos
====================================================
*/

export interface Props {
  authorName: string;
}

const { authorName } = Astro.props;
---

<section data-editor class="hidden" data-default-author={authorName}>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
    <button
      data-cancel
      type="button"
      class="mb-6 inline-flex min-h-11 items-center rounded-md text-sm font-semibold text-stone-600 transition hover:text-stone-950 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-4 focus-visible:outline-stone-950 dark:text-stone-300 dark:hover:text-white"
    >
      ← Volver al listado
    </button>

    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-400">Editor</p>
      <h1
        data-editor-title
        class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-stone-950 dark:text-white sm:text-4xl"
      >
        Nueva reflexión
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400">
        Organiza la idea, revisa cómo se sentirá al leerla y publícala cuando esté lista.
      </p>
    </div>

    <form data-editor-form class="mt-8 grid gap-6" novalidate>
      <input data-id type="hidden" />

      <fieldset class="rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 bg-white p-5 dark:border-stone-800 dark:bg-stone-950 sm:p-7">
        <legend class="px-2 text-lg font-semibold text-stone-950 dark:text-white">1. Idea principal</legend>
        <div class="mt-3 grid gap-5">
          <div>
            <label for="reflection-title" class="text-sm font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">
              Título del artículo
            </label>
            <p id="reflection-title-help" class="mt-1 text-sm leading-5 text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400">
              Invita a descubrir la idea sin repetir exactamente la frase de portada.
            </p>
            <input
              id="reflection-title"
              data-title
              required
              aria-describedby="reflection-title-help editorial-repetition-warning"
              placeholder="Ejemplo: Cómo dejar de vivir desde las heridas"
              class="mt-2 h-12 w-full rounded-xl border border-stone-300 bg-white px-4 text-base text-stone-950 outline-none transition placeholder:text-stone-400 focus:border-amber-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-700/15 dark:border-stone-700 dark:bg-stone-900 dark:text-white"
            />
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 sm:flex-row sm:items-end sm:justify-between sm:gap-4">
              <label for="reflection-quote" class="text-sm font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">
                Frase destacada de la portada
              </label>
              <span data-quote-count class="shrink-0 text-xs text-stone-400">0 / 160 recomendado</span>
            </div>
            <p id="reflection-quote-help" class="mt-1 text-sm leading-5 text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400">
              Es la idea breve que aparecerá sobre la imagen y que las personas podrán recordar o compartir.
            </p>
            <textarea
              id="reflection-quote"
              data-quote
              required
              rows="4"
              aria-describedby="reflection-quote-help editorial-repetition-warning"
              placeholder="Ejemplo: No eres lo que te pasó. Eres lo que decides construir con ello."
              class="mt-2 min-h-28 w-full resize-y rounded-xl border border-stone-300 bg-white p-4 text-base leading-6 text-stone-950 outline-none transition placeholder:text-stone-400 focus:border-amber-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-700/15 dark:border-stone-700 dark:bg-stone-900 dark:text-white"
            ></textarea>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="reflection-author" class="text-sm font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">
              Autor de la cita <span class="font-normal text-stone-400">(opcional)</span>
            </label>
            <p id="reflection-author-help" class="mt-1 text-sm leading-5 text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400">
              Déjalo vacío si la frase es tuya. En ese caso se utilizará {authorName}.
            </p>
            <input
              id="reflection-author"
              data-author
              aria-describedby="reflection-author-help"
              placeholder="Ejemplo: Viktor Frankl"
              class="mt-2 h-12 w-full rounded-xl border border-stone-300 bg-white px-4 text-base text-stone-950 outline-none transition placeholder:text-stone-400 focus:border-amber-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-700/15 dark:border-stone-700 dark:bg-stone-900 dark:text-white"
            />
          </div>

          <p
            id="editorial-repetition-warning"
            data-repetition-warning
            class="hidden rounded-xl border border-amber-300 bg-amber-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm leading-5 text-amber-900 dark:border-amber-800 dark:bg-amber-950/40 dark:text-amber-200"
            role="status"
          >
            El título y la frase de portada expresan exactamente lo mismo. Puedes guardar el borrador, pero deberás
            diferenciarlos antes de publicar.
          </p>
        </div>
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset class="rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 bg-white p-5 dark:border-stone-800 dark:bg-stone-950 sm:p-7">
        <legend class="px-2 text-lg font-semibold text-stone-950 dark:text-white">2. Imagen principal</legend>
        <p id="reflection-image-help" class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400">
          Usa una imagen horizontal limpia, sin texto, firma ni logotipos. El sitio colocará la frase mediante HTML.
        </p>
        <input
          id="reflection-image"
          data-image
          type="file"
          accept="image/jpeg,image/png,image/webp"
          aria-describedby="reflection-image-help"
          class="sr-only"
        />

        <div
          data-image-empty
          class="mt-4 flex min-h-40 flex-col items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-dashed border-stone-300 bg-stone-50 px-5 py-8 text-center dark:border-stone-700 dark:bg-stone-900/60"
        >
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-stone-700 dark:text-stone-200">
            La imagen se verá aquí antes de guardarla.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-stone-500">JPEG, PNG o WebP · preferiblemente 16:9</p>
          <button
            data-choose-image
            type="button"
            class="mt-4 inline-flex min-h-11 items-center rounded-full border border-stone-300 px-5 text-sm font-semibold text-stone-800 transition hover:border-stone-500 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-3 focus-visible:outline-stone-950 dark:border-stone-700 dark:text-stone-100"
          >
            Seleccionar imagen
          </button>
        </div>

        <div data-image-preview-container class="mt-4 hidden">
          <div
            class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 bg-stone-100 dark:border-stone-800 dark:bg-stone-900"
          >
            <img
              data-image-preview
              src=""
              alt="Vista previa de la imagen principal seleccionada"
              class="aspect-video w-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="mt-3 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
            <div class="min-w-0 text-sm">
              <p data-image-name class="truncate font-medium text-stone-800 dark:text-stone-100"></p>
              <p data-image-size class="mt-0.5 text-xs text-stone-500"></p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <button
                data-choose-image
                type="button"
                class="inline-flex min-h-11 items-center rounded-full border border-stone-300 px-4 text-sm font-semibold transition hover:border-stone-500 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-3 focus-visible:outline-stone-950 dark:border-stone-700"
              >
                Cambiar imagen
              </button>
              <button
                data-remove-image
                type="button"
                class="min-h-11 rounded-full px-4 text-sm font-semibold text-red-700 transition hover:bg-red-50 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-3 focus-visible:outline-red-700 dark:text-red-300 dark:hover:bg-red-950/40"
              >
                Eliminar
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset class="rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 bg-white p-5 dark:border-stone-800 dark:bg-stone-950 sm:p-7">
        <legend class="px-2 text-lg font-semibold text-stone-950 dark:text-white">3. Contenido</legend>
        <label for="reflection-body" class="mt-3 block text-sm font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">
          Desarrollo de la reflexión
        </label>
        <p id="reflection-body-help" class="mt-1 text-sm leading-5 text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400">
          Escribe con calma. Utiliza párrafos breves y separa cada idea con una línea en blanco.
        </p>
        <textarea
          id="reflection-body"
          data-body
          required
          rows="16"
          aria-describedby="reflection-body-help reflection-reading-time"
          placeholder="Empieza a desarrollar aquí la idea que quieres compartir…"
          class="mt-3 min-h-80 w-full resize-y rounded-xl border border-stone-300 bg-white p-4 text-base leading-7 text-stone-950 outline-none transition placeholder:text-stone-400 focus:border-amber-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-700/15 dark:border-stone-700 dark:bg-stone-900 dark:text-white"
        ></textarea>
        <p id="reflection-reading-time" data-reading-time class="mt-2 text-xs text-stone-500">
          1 min de lectura estimada
        </p>
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset class="rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 bg-white p-5 dark:border-stone-800 dark:bg-stone-950 sm:p-7">
        <legend class="px-2 text-lg font-semibold text-stone-950 dark:text-white">4. Publicación</legend>
        <div class="mt-3 grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <label for="reflection-status" class="text-sm font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100"
              >Estado</label
            >
            <select
              id="reflection-status"
              data-status
              class="mt-2 h-12 w-full rounded-xl border border-stone-300 bg-white px-4 text-base outline-none transition focus:border-amber-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-700/15 dark:border-stone-700 dark:bg-stone-900"
            >
              <option value="draft">Borrador</option>
              <option value="published">Publicada</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="reflection-date" class="text-sm font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">
              Publicar el
            </label>
            <p id="reflection-date-help" class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-stone-500">
              Puedes publicar ahora o programar una fecha futura.
            </p>
            <input
              id="reflection-date"
              data-date
              type="datetime-local"
              required
              aria-describedby="reflection-date-help"
              class="mt-2 h-12 w-full rounded-xl border border-stone-300 bg-white px-4 text-base outline-none transition focus:border-amber-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-700/15 dark:border-stone-700 dark:bg-stone-900"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <details data-advanced class="mt-5 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800">
          <summary
            class="flex min-h-12 cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between px-4 text-sm font-semibold marker:content-none focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-stone-950"
          >
            Opciones avanzadas <span aria-hidden="true" class="text-stone-400">＋</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="border-t border-stone-200 p-4 dark:border-stone-800">
            <label for="reflection-slug" class="text-sm font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">
              URL del artículo
            </label>
            <p id="reflection-slug-help" class="mt-1 text-sm leading-5 text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400">
              Se genera automáticamente a partir del título. Normalmente no necesitas modificarla.
            </p>
            <div
              class="mt-2 flex min-h-12 items-center rounded-xl border border-stone-300 bg-stone-50 focus-within:border-amber-700 focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-amber-700/15 dark:border-stone-700 dark:bg-stone-900"
            >
              <span class="pl-4 text-sm text-stone-400" aria-hidden="true">/reflexiones/</span>
              <input
                id="reflection-slug"
                data-slug
                required
                aria-describedby="reflection-slug-help reflection-url-preview"
                placeholder="url-del-articulo"
                class="h-11 min-w-0 flex-1 bg-transparent pr-4 text-sm text-stone-950 outline-none dark:text-white"
              />
            </div>
            <p id="reflection-url-preview" data-url-preview class="mt-2 break-all text-xs text-stone-500"></p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </fieldset>

      <div
        class="rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 bg-white/95 p-3 shadow-[0_16px_50px_rgba(28,25,23,0.12)] backdrop-blur-xl dark:border-stone-800 dark:bg-stone-950/95 sm:sticky sm:bottom-3 sm:z-20"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col-reverse gap-2 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-end">
          <button
            data-save-draft
            type="button"
            class="min-h-11 rounded-full border border-stone-300 px-5 text-sm font-semibold text-stone-800 transition hover:border-stone-500 disabled:cursor-wait disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-3 focus-visible:outline-stone-950 dark:border-stone-700 dark:text-stone-100"
          >
            Guardar borrador
          </button>
          <button
            data-preview
            type="button"
            class="min-h-11 rounded-full px-5 text-sm font-semibold text-stone-700 transition hover:bg-stone-100 disabled:cursor-wait disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-3 focus-visible:outline-stone-950 dark:text-stone-200 dark:hover:bg-stone-900"
          >
            Vista previa
          </button>
          <button
            data-publish
            type="submit"
            class="min-h-11 rounded-full bg-stone-950 px-6 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-stone-800 disabled:cursor-wait disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-3 focus-visible:outline-stone-950 dark:bg-white dark:text-stone-950 dark:hover:bg-stone-200"
          >
            Publicar
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>

  <dialog
    data-preview-dialog
    aria-labelledby="admin-preview-title"
    class="m-auto max-h-[94dvh] w-[min(72rem,calc(100%-1.5rem))] overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-stone-200 bg-stone-950 p-0 text-white shadow-2xl backdrop:bg-stone-950/80 dark:border-stone-800"
  >
    <div class="flex max-h-[94dvh] flex-col">
      <header class="flex min-h-16 items-center justify-between border-b border-white/10 px-5 sm:px-7">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-stone-400">Vista previa editorial</p>
          <h2 id="admin-preview-title" class="sr-only">Vista previa de la reflexión</h2>
        </div>
        <button
          data-close-preview
          type="button"
          class="min-h-11 rounded-full border border-white/15 px-4 text-sm font-semibold transition hover:bg-white/10 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-white"
        >
          Cerrar
        </button>
      </header>
      <div class="overflow-y-auto p-4 sm:p-7 lg:p-10">
        <article class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
          <div
            data-preview-hero
            class="relative aspect-[16/10] overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-stone-900 sm:aspect-video"
          >
            <img data-preview-image src="" alt="" class="hidden h-full w-full object-cover" />
            <div
              class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-stone-950/85 via-stone-950/15 to-transparent"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
            </div>
            <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 p-5 sm:p-9">
              <blockquote
                data-preview-quote
                class="max-w-3xl text-balance text-2xl font-semibold leading-tight sm:text-4xl"
              >
              </blockquote>
              <p data-preview-author class="mt-3 text-sm text-white/75"></p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mx-auto max-w-[42rem] py-8 sm:py-12">
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-400">
              <time data-preview-date></time><span aria-hidden="true"> · </span><span data-preview-time></span>
            </p>
            <h1
              data-preview-title
              class="mt-4 text-balance text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-5xl"
            >
            </h1>
            <div data-preview-body class="mt-8 space-y-5 text-lg leading-8 text-stone-300"></div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </dialog>
</section>

<style>
  [data-preview-dialog]::backdrop {
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    [data-preview-dialog]::backdrop {
      backdrop-filter: none;
    }
  }
</style>
